---
import {Image} from "astro:assets"
import Reporting from "../../assets/reporting.svg"
import Approved from "../../assets/approved.svg"
import Team from "../../assets/hierarchy.svg"
import Scalable from "../../assets/puzzle.svg"
---

<section class="container mx-auto py-20 md:py-40 px-4">
  <h2 class="lg:text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold !leading-tight">Creative Talent Recruiting<br />Made <span class="px-2 bg-brand-primary rounded-lg leading-none">Super Simple</span></h2>
  <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-rows-2 gap-4">
    <div class="relative col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col">
      <div class="absolute z-10 bg-brand-dark top-0 bottom-0 right-0 left-0 rounded-md"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 h-full relative z-20 py-12 px-8 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-md hover:-translate-x-2 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200">
        <Image alt="scalable hiring" src={Scalable} class="h-12 w-12 md:h-20 md:w-20"/>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 font-semibold">Instant, Scalable Hiring</p>
          <p>With our subscriptions, you can scale your team up or down as needed with just a click, allowing you to build your perfect team with us, and only scale as you need to grow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col ">
      <div class="absolute z-10 bg-brand-dark top-0 bottom-0 right-0 left-0 rounded-md"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 relative z-20 h-full py-12 px-8 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-md hover:-translate-x-2 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200">
        <Image alt="scalable hiring" src={Approved} class="h-12 w-12 md:h-16 md:w-16"/>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 font-semibold">Vetted and Talented Experts</p>
          <p>Our team is full of diverse, highly skilled creatives, ready to get to work on your projects. We thoroughly vet all of our talent for the best candidates.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col ">
      <div class="absolute z-10 bg-brand-dark top-0 bottom-0 right-0 left-0 rounded-md"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 relative z-20 h-full py-12 px-8  bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-md hover:-translate-x-2 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200">
        <Image alt="scalable hiring" src={Team} class="h-12 w-12 md:h-16 md:w-16"/>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 font-semibold">Fully Managed Teams</p>
          <p>You get a dedicated PM that handles delegating all tasks to the perfect team member. No more neding to manage a web of contractors and freelancers to get work done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative col-span-2 lg:col-span-1 flex flex-col">
      <div class="absolute z-10 bg-brand-dark top-0 bottom-0 right-0 left-0 rounded-md"></div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 relative h-full z-20 py-12 px-8 bg-white border-2 border-black rounded-md hover:-translate-x-2 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-200">
        <Image alt="scalable hiring" src={Reporting} class="h-12 w-12 md:h-16 md:w-16"/>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4 font-semibold">Daily Reporting and Updates</p>
        <p>Stay up to date on the progress of all of your work through daily progress reporting and insight, and rest easily knowing our team is helping to propel your business forward.</p>
        </div>
      </div> 
    </div>
  </div>
</section>